Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent in 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' status across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time for cases following 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time it takes for a declaration to be resubmitted after being 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of cases that involve 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and next activity in the process
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time to reach 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' from the start of the case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent in 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Request Payment' for cases that continue in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Payment Handled' for cases that are successfully resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time for a case to be finalized after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' before being approved or finalized
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case
